Emails that we forget to send, voice messages that we never receive, innocent lies that almost annoy us more: these are things that “embellish” the everyday life of a workplace.
The question is whether to get used to these troubles or take up the challenge and consciously avoid ambiguous situations, causing trouble to others.
Examples.
