There are no good ways to stop the spread of gossip.
Who did what, with whom?
Or why?
Don’t tell everyone your information (assumptions) about your colleagues’ privacy!
If a colleague shares his intimate secrets with you, do not abuse his trust!
Bury the shared information in yourself and do not discuss it with your colleagues in its absence, even if your colleagues are also aware of it.
